text: Pál Tuska (born 29 January 1957) is a Hungarian equestrian. He competed in the team eventing at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Hungary Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Törökszentmiklós
